ster.avif?t=1763616718\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266800/extras/7be9ac60d67429fa1c6414837a212e19.webm?t=1763616718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266800/extras/7be9ac60d67429fa1c6414837a212e19.mp4?t=1763616718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>15 Live2D CG with over 40 artwork<br></li><li>Over 2000 lines of dialog, fully and professionally voice acted<br></li><li>Beautiful background artwork<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266800/extras/99349c2bc44b41b3fc61f370a6a02133.avif?t=1763616718\" width=600 height=242 /></span><br></li><li>Catchy tune and upbeat tempo music<br></li><li>Many items to unlock and collect as gifts</li></ul>",
